---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"lint\", \"--help\"])"
---
Report lint violations across the project

Usage: hpds lint [OPTIONS] [PATHS]...

Arguments:
  [PATHS]...  Files or directories to lint (default: the whole project)

Options:
      --fix              Apply safe autofixes first, then report what remains
  -v, --verbose          Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
  -q, --quiet            Suppress all output except errors
      --no-color         Disable colored output
      --config <PATH>    Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml
  -h, --help             Print help
